collections.name: Looking for you in the rain
Looking for you in the rain
Scriptura Primitiva
collections.description:
Digital primitivism for future generations

I saw a woman, a beautiful woman. Her posture was that of a Greek goddess. She cut through the crowd like a glass shard. She smelled of an electric shock.

“Do you have a dream, kid?” she asked, grinning.

Her eyes gleamed in the halogen glow. This human baseline fascination with fire.

I felt molecules shivering under the surface. I couldn’t tell if it was her or something deeper, buried inside me. I suddenly thought of the past.
I imagined being a caveman, leaving red ochre marks on a wall with my bare hands. This human baseline desire to transfix its presence through a picture.

Or was it the future?

The history is a looping glitch, and I can feel the gap between me—consolidating primitives on the blockchain—and our descendants, born in hundreds of years.


---

Scriptura Primitiva is a hybrid JavaScript Canvas/WebGL generative application. It accepts a series of digitally created abstract paintings as input to mix, slice, and distort them within algorithmically bounded randomness. Press Command + S (macOS) or Ctrl + S (Windows/Linux) to save the render as a PNG.

collections.name: DoctorGlasses
collections.description:
Welcome to DoctorGlasses®, an innovative NFT collection that redefines digital art by drawing inspiration from the legendary pop art movement, with a particular focus on the bold, vibrant aesthetics of Andy Warhol.
The Vision: DoctorGlasses® aims to bring the iconic visual language of Warhol's art into the digital age. Through the lens of blockchain technology, we are offering a collection of unique, limited-edition digital artworks that explore the themes of mass production, celebrity culture, and consumerism – all central to Warhol's ethos.

What is DoctorGlasses®? DoctorGlasses® is a series of digitally-created artworks that take classic pop culture references and reimagine them through a modern, digital lens. Each piece in the collection mirrors Warhol’s technique of repetition and color manipulation but with a futuristic twist. From reinterpretations of famous icons to bold, colorful abstract pieces, every NFT captures the essence of pop art while embracing the unique possibilities of the NFT space.
